original_title: Vantawhite Pages Almanac Issue 1: The Black Square
overview: 2048. A day in the life of some of Earth's inhabitants. It's the century of commercial use for Black Square, and "Vantawhite Pages" is the world's largest company. An almanac of human history has been created on Vantawhite Pages using ink from Vantablack.
title: Vantawhite Pages Almanac Issue 1: The Black Square
